    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Solid, Reliable & Ready to Roll \u2014 A Great Everyday Driver! This well-maintained vehicle is in good condition and delivers exactly what you need in a dependable used car. The exterior has the minor scuffs and light wear you'd expect from a car that's been genuinely used, but nothing that takes away from its solid appeal. Under the hood, it runs smoothly and handles daily driving with ease. The interior is clean and comfortable, showing normal signs of use but well cared for overall. If you're looking for a trustworthy vehicle at a fair price, this one is well worth a look!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
